            <p class="astro-privacy-policy">Furthermore, if you are a minor under 18 years old living in California and have a registered account with our Service, you are empowered to ask for the deletion of any undesirable data that you have publicly posted on our Service. For such removal requests, please contact us with the email linked to your account, confirming your residence in California. While we will ensure such data is not publicly visible on our Service, be aware that complete and exhaustive removal from our systems may not be feasible.</p>
